<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/676525-i-m-confused-the-copy-of-divine-secrets">I&#39;m confused. The copy of Divine Secrets I&#39;m reading says Little Altars came out first, but this says it&#39;s Ya-Ya #2. Are both those things correct? I&#39;m reading Divine Secrets first, but do some people read Little Altars first?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_676525'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6697.Little_Altars_Everywhere">like</a></span>

