              <span id="reviewTextContainer2645684593" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8932697044415467952">This one gives a closer look at Sidda &amp; Vivi&apos;s nuclear family, and I loved it just as much as &quot;Divine Secrets&quot;. Reading this book in public always turned heads, because I&apos;d crack up laughing, or gasp angrily, or burst out in tears, or do all three.</span>
  <span id="freeText8932697044415467952" style="display:none">This one gives a closer look at Sidda &amp; Vivi's nuclear family, and I loved it just as much as "Divine Secrets". Reading this book in public always turned heads, because I'd crack up laughing, or gasp angrily, or burst out in tears, or do all three.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8932697044415467952" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


